data.description:
THIS IS IT! Absolutely stunning, one of a kind custom home in a phenomenal location with incredible, unobstructed mountain views. Great, flowing floorplan with the main level featuring an attractive, large living room with wood ceilings, and looking out to the back patio with views and inground pebble tech pool. Also on this level is the kitchen that has newer appliances and granite countertops. The primary suite is also downstairs and has a remodeled attach bathroom w/ garden tub and shower. Another front living area, a 1/2 bathroom, and spacious laundry room encompass this floor. Upstairs are 3 more bedrooms and a full bathroom. All bedrooms are well placed and feature plenty of room for larger beds. The yard is your own private oasis w/ landscaped grounds, pool, views and a spa. Home starts here!

LAST OFFER FELL OUT OF CONTRACT WITH NO FAULT OF THE SELLER.
